    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Just call <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/Math.html#abs-int-\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Math.abs</a>. For example:</p>\n<pre><code>int x = Math.abs(-5);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Which will set <code>x</code> to <code>5</code>.</p>\n<p>Note that if you pass <code>Integer.MIN_VALUE</code>, the same value (still negative) will be returned, as the range of <code>int</code> does not allow the positive equivalent to be represented.</p>\n"
  }, {
